Huh?  As I stated before, this guild takes great pride in the respect we show others, both in the guild and outside it.  That is reflected by others speaking up on our behalf and by the relative absence of any negative remarks ANYWHERE about PC.  Again, outside of isolated instances, you are simply not going to be seeing signs of us as an antagonistic, problem-causing group of people.  <br>
